videos.title: Duskmourn Spoilers  Unblockable 101 for Three????  MTG
videos.description:
Today as we reach the end of week one of Duskmourn spoilers we get a 10/1 for just three mana, and it can't even be blocked! Plus our green leyline, some nerdy counters shenanigans, Demonic card draw and more! Let's discuss!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
